        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-6dcb6dcb-3f7c-4675-96b6-81612baf9462">
                The Minister of Defence (Mr. A. V. Alexander)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-6dcb6dcb-3f7c-4675-96b6-81612baf9462" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
