                Mr. Kirkwood  (Dumbarton Burghs)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-2e8c3a25-508f-4e97-a84d-44fcd7b3b52f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
