                Sir J. Anderson
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-a5dca7c8-7977-4abb-a09d-d14df486a97f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
